00:31:45.669 --> 00:31:49.940
&gt;&gt;Sandra: Cool, last question before I open
up to questions. Tell us something about yourself

00:31:49.940 --> 00:31:55.899
that we would find surprising about you.
&gt;&gt;Alexis: That I balance a career mostly in

00:31:55.899 --> 00:32:04.659
fashion by making sure that I do at least
a one or two week excursion, camping excursion

00:32:04.659 --> 00:32:09.340
every year, usually in Alaska. So I feel like
