00:35:48.140 --> 00:35:51.570
and I was just wondering you're very positive
and I love that and I love your confidence

00:35:51.570 --> 00:35:56.100
and I like your advice. But I was just wondering
if there was anything that you or your co-founder

00:35:56.100 --> 00:36:03.180
were really afraid of? Because it seems to
me it was obvious there was a target audience

00:36:03.180 --> 00:36:07.010
for this. So that wasn't really a fear like
