00:36:07.010 --> 00:36:10.450
I was just wondering if there is anything
that you were afraid of taking the leap to

00:36:10.450 --> 00:36:12.961
start your own business?
&gt;&gt;Alexis: Well, in terms of the idea, there

00:36:12.961 --> 00:36:17.230
was a great possibility that first morning
